  <brief_title>International HIT-MED Registry (I-HIT-MED)</brief_title>
  <official_title>International HIT-MED Registry (I-HIT-MED) for Children, Adolescents, and Adults With Medulloblastoma, Ependymoma, Pineoblastoma, CNS-primitive Neuroectodermal Tumours</official_title>
